Publication Date: November 7, 2013

It was the year 1885 when Emilie Baetes lost everything. Her mother, her lifestyle, and Elizabeth, her one true love... Now, it is 1895, and Emilie has the chance to gain part of her past back. Disguised as a man, Emilie flees London in hopes of finding her beloved once more.   However, nothing ever goes as planned, and Emilie finds herself forced to confront the one part of herself that she has spent her entire life trying to hide.
